summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation; accepting a donation to The City of Seattle of certain real property located adjacent to the Duwamish Head Greenbelt, legally described as portions of Government Lot 5, Section 13, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, from H.A. and Margaret J. Winquist, husband and wife; authorizing payment of certain costs in connection with the donation; and placing the property under the jurisdiction of the Department of Parks and Recreation for open space, park and recreation purposes.
